p968
sg5
VThe sound quality and noise-cancelling feature is unmatched by any competing brand in my opinion. They come with a nice carrying case for travel, and fold up easily to fit in. They are simple to use and they even come with a AAA battery for the noise-cancelling feature. Don't forget to turn it off once you're done with them! My only complaint about these is in regards to the Volume Adjustment buttons. They are only compatible on Apple devices. If you're using these on a PC or Android device, the sound quality and noise cancelling feature will be fine, but you won't be able to adjust the volume using the headphones. It is annoying that Bose would be that short-sighted, but it is what it is. If the adjustment buttons worked on all devices, I would give this 5 stars. Overall, I would recommend these headphones regardless of the device you're using.
