VI seriously love these noise canceling headphones. I bought these for my first international flight to the Philippines. The flight was 17 hours total and I was worried about trying to sleep with the engine noise. These headphones entirely eliminate the engine noise in an aircraft. I wore them the entire 17 hours while I was in the air and my ears never felt crushed or sensitive. The headphones are incredibly comfortable to wear for extended amounts of time.I flew on the Boeing 787 for one leg of the journey and while wearing these head phones and watching a movie in the LED display, I even forgot I was on an airplane for a couple hours. The comfort and effectiveness of these head phones made my flight almost easy. My girlfriend loved them as well so I'll be buying her some of these for our next long flight.These headphones satisfied all of my needs, but I want to be clear about what they won't do. These headphones won't stop you from hearing a crying baby. They won't stop you from hearing your seat-mate talking. The headphones seem to most effectively cancel our consistent noises such as fans, engine noise, or keyboard typing. Noises that spike such as conversation, knocking, or coughing can still be heard. Albeit, even these noises are slightly dampened.
